cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or its outputs, please cite it as below."
title: "iwv-bcm-et-eval: Actual Evapotranspiration Evaluation over the Indian Wells Valley, CA"
abstract: >-
  Scripts and analyses for comparing multiple remote sensing and modeled
  actual evapotranspiration (AET) products against the USGS Reitz ET
  reference dataset over the Indian Wells Valley (IWV) Basin Characterization
  Model (BCM) calibration basins and sub-basins for water years 2001-2015.
type: software
authors:
